summary: ITC Mena Alas is calling regarding a promotion they are running for ESET Mobile Security. The customer, Fathima Shamir, has a Nippy Nooddy Rose Cover package and is instructed to follow the instructions in the package to be eligible for a gift. The package needs to be scanned for a link to be sent to a WhatsApp account, where a video of eating noodles needs to be uploaded for verification. The most important details are to beat the S.T.R.O., B.S.T., and sixes, and to include the video in the WhatsApp message. The customer should be patient as the gift will be granted if they qualify, and they can also check the website ww.imova.cool for more information. The call disconnects abruptly at the end.
